{"tid":620503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國西部城市明斯特（Munster）一貨車衝向人群，初步傳出逾30死傷","createTime":"2018-04-07T15:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T17:41:16.000Z","uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"78000e6546ca9f5ee8258093759a4f653da317a4","tid":620503,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180407/s00005/471cf616e0b5e3d6ab607792042d130e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180407%2Fs00005%2F471cf616e0b5e3d6ab607792042d130e.jpg&h=a2178ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國西部城市明斯特（Munster），當地時間星期六下午，一輛貨車衝上行人路撞向人群，初步消息指釀成最少3死超過30傷，肇事司機事後則向自己開槍，有照片拍得現場桌椅一片狼籍。當地警方事後已封鎖現場，並循恐怖襲擊等方向調查。<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180407/s00005/1523115024110?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180407%2Fs00005%2F1523115024110%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=pl5aEsuenyudVV7cn01DNTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=78f721aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180407%2Fs00005%2F1523115024110%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=da41e26d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180407/s00005/1523115024110?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"d889cfe9170d701a7613c80fae8a226ac7b5555b","tid":620503,"uid":4783,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"德國又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超級大左膠州分都俾人開波，唔知個到既居民情何以堪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d903b49f17afae566e75bb99eeda348475017ab1","tid":620503,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"Die Wel